English: It's kind of like if I want to get rid of x, well I have to divide by x.
In this case I have degrees, so I want to divide by degrees.
But if I'm multiplying this in, I've got to make sure it's pi radians on top.
Chinese: 这有点像：如果我想去掉x，那我就必须除以x。
在这种情况下，我有度数，所以我希望除以度数。
但如果我在做乘法时把这东西加进来，就必须确保分子是π弧度。
